did.head: Descriptive Summary
did.unittitle: Stark, Samuel, collector. Film and stage stars : photographs,

repository.label: Repository
repository.corpname: Stanford University. Libraries. Dept. of Special Collections and University Archives.

did.abstract: The collection includes some 1,246 names are represented, many of these with more than one photograph. The bulk of the dated photos are between 1915 and 1940, though there are many more recent that are undated.

userestrict.head: Publication Rights
userestrict.p: Property rights reside with the repository. Literary rights reside with the creators of the documents or their heirs. To obtain permission to publish or reproduce, please contact the Public Services Librarian of the Dept. of Special Collections.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Samuel Stark Film and stage stars : photographs. MSS PHOTO 171. Dept. of Special Collections, Stanford University Libraries, Stanford, Calif.

custodhist.head: Provenance
custodhist.p: Originally formed part of the Stanford Libraries' Theater Collection.

scopecontent.head: Collection Scope and Content Summary
scopecontent.p: Some 1,246 names are represented, many of these with more than one photograph. The bulk of the dated photos are between 1915 and 1940, though there are many more recent that are undated.

controlaccess.p: The following terms have been used to index the description of this collection in the library's online public access catalog.
